# Draft:Call of War

Call of War, also known as Call of War 1942, Call of War: World War 2, Call of War: World War II, 1942: Call of War, Supremacy: Call of War 1942, is a game by Bytro Labs that simulates World War II. It is a Massively multiplayer online game, with games in Real-time or 4x speed.
